    {
      "id": "2048024942286147822",
      "text": "Comprehensive Multilingual Text Rendering：\nBetter glyph accuracy, more consistent typography, and cleaner layouts even in complex compositions.\nIt handles mixed-language scenarios more gracefully as well.\nIf you’re building posters, UI mockups, ads, or anything text-heavy, this should feel like a meaningful step forward.🪄",
      "created_at": "Sat Apr 25 13:02:51 +0000 2026",
      "url": "https://x.com/Alibaba_Qwen/status/2048024942286147822",
      "author": {
        "user_name": "Alibaba_Qwen",
        "name": "Qwen"
      },
      "metrics": {
        "likes": 30,
        "retweets": 4,
        "replies": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2048024937999577533",
      "text": "Substantially Elevated Visual Fidelity：\nWe’ve made major improvements in texture detail, lighting coherence, and material realism. This applies across both photorealistic scenes and stylized outputs, so you don’t have to trade realism for style anymore.\nYes, this is not a selfie.📸",
      "created_at": "Sat Apr 25 13:02:50 +0000 2026",
      "url": "https://x.com/Alibaba_Qwen/status/2048024937999577533",
      "author": {
        "user_name": "Alibaba_Qwen",
