    },
    {
      "id": "2048024933805244779",
      "text": "Sharper Instruction Following: \nThe model now adheres more closely to prompt semantics, especially for complex compositions. Better handling of multiple objects, spatial relationships and attribute binding\nYes, this is not a screenshot.📲 https://t.co/Bjs1zgT4mF",
